{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BroadcastChannel.onmessage","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name\"><code>name</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><em><code>message</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>当 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a> 接收到类型为 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a> 的 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/message\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">message</a></code> 事件时，<code><strong>BroadcastChannel.onmessage</strong></code>&nbsp;属性可以指定一个函数，作为该事件对应的事件处理程序来执行。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 此特性在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 中可用</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>channel</em>.onmessage = <em>function</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>function</code>&nbsp;是一个用户自定义函数的名称，不带 <code>()</code> 后续或参数；也可以是一个匿名函数，如 <code>function(event) {...}</code>。一个事件处理程序通常只有一个参数，包含了类型为 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a> 的事件。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>bc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onmessage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">ev</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message event received!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">备注</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/comms.html#handler-broadcastchannel-onmessage\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">BroadcastChannel.onmessage</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.BroadcastChannel.onmessage","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>一种在不同浏览器上下文之间通信的重量级方案：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a>。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"当 BroadcastChannel 接收到类型为 MessageEvent 的 message 事件时，BroadcastChannel.onmessage 属性可以指定一个函数，作为该事件对应的事件处理程序来执行。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BroadcastChannel.onmessage","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/broadcastchannel/message_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/broadcastchannel/message_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event","title":"BroadcastChannel.onmessage"}],"pageTitle":"BroadcastChannel.onmessage | MDN","noIndexing":true}}